headline: Barclays upgrades Dell on strong AI server orders, enterprise recovery
summary: Investing.com -- Barclays has upgraded Dell Technologies (NYSE:DELL) to Overweight (OW) from Equal Weight amid growing confidence in the company’s position across AI servers as well as improving opportunities in enterprise server and storage markets.
